{"id":22126,"title":"Visualization of the meibomian glands by means of noncontact mobile-type meibography (Meibopen) in a 16-year-old girl with unilateral marginal staphylococcal keratitis.","abstract":"Marked alterations of the meibomian glands in a patient with marginal staphylococcal keratitis can be seen using the noncontact mobile-type meibography system, a simple and convenient tool that facilitates visualization of meibomian glands throughout the entire upper and lower eyelids. ","date":"2014-02-26","categories":"Bacterial Infections and Mycoses","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24568999","annotations":[{"name":"Visualization (computer graphics)","weight":0.12131,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Visualization_(computer_graphics)"},{"name":"Keratitis","weight":0.0342852,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Keratitis"},{"name":"Meibomian gland","weight":0.0342852,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Meibomian_gland"},{"name":"Tool","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tool"},{"name":"Gland","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gland"},{"name":"Unilateralism","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Unilateralism"},{"name":"Star Wars Tales Volume 6","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Star_Wars_Tales_Volume_6"},{"name":"Patient","weight":0.0157947,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Patient"},{"name":"Eyelid","weight":0.0157947,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eyelid"},{"name":"Staphylococcus","weight":0.0148276,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Staphylococcus"}]}
